snippet.title: OYASUMII - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST OYASUMII ON STEAM NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3033520/OYASUMII/

Join the Discord ►    https://discord.gg/dPtJEK5FGQ
Follow my Twitter ► https://x.com/neoproject_st

Relive the nostalgia with OYASUMII, a horror and exploration game inspired by PSX and N64 classics. Enter liminal spaces and face surreal terrors in an adventure that challenges your skills and sanity. Are you ready to relive the golden age of video games with OYASUMII?
Coming soon!

sound by  Unayzah

sound by No Shade
https://www.instagram.com/no_sh4d3.exe/

#OYASUMII #IndieHorror
